reviewText: These were all great enjoyable movies.  Having watched so many movies over the holidays, it's difficult to remember details of each of them, but overall they were great.  No complaints at all.  They are movies that we will enjoy watching every year over the Christmas holidays.  The quality was great, and I would highly recommend them either for yourself or to give as a gift.
Title: Holiday Collector's Set V.5
